                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Bremsstrahlung was produced by irradiating",
                "niobium foil with thickness of 7 mu-m (3.4mg/cm2)",
                "with electron beam of kinetic energy 13.0+-0.1 MeV",
                "A narrow photon beam was formed by an Al collimator",
